Package cz.cvut.fel.omo.smartfarm.state.equipment

Class OnState

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.omo.smartfarm.state.equipment.OnState
All Implemented Interfaces:
EquipmentState
public class OnState extends Object implements EquipmentState
Represents the state of equipment when it is turned on. In this state, the equipment can perform actions and transition to other states such as off or broken.
